Package: fawir
Type: Package
Title: Football Analytics with R
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-01-28
Authors@R: person(given = "Guillermo", family = "Vinue", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "guillermovinue@gmail.com")
Description: Collection of tools to work with football data. Functions available are related to friendly 
	web scraping, data management and visualization. Data were obtained from <https:///www.pesmaster.com/>, 
	following <https://www.pesmaster.com/robots.txt>. There is also a player matching algorithm for
	recruitment purposes.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://www.uv.es/vivigui/, https://www.R-project.org 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, ggpubr, ggtext, janitor, magrittr, polite, purrr, RcppParallel, RhpcBLASctl, readr, robotstxt, rvest, stringr, text2vec, tidyr, tidytext  
Suggests: knitr, markdown, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Encoding: UTF-8
